{"type":"message","id":"b81a6bbe","parentId":"d0990dc6","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:04:33.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK this one works but requires a valid symbol. Let me try with Chinese stock format. Actually Twelve Data likely doesn't support Chinese A-shares directly. Let me check what other options we have.Actually, the issue is that the iFinD tool (同花顺) isn't working due to a configuration error. This is likely an issue on QVeris's side with their iFinD integration. Let me try to find an alternative.\n\nLet me search for \"Sina\" or \"Tencent\" or \"Netease\" Chinese stock data APIs, or maybe search for a different approach.","thinkingSignature":"e37f123532dacaee3a14efa7d8e4bd2ed524748a182c25602637ea8b37e571c7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_evhl4egmuegu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace && node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs search \"Chinese A股 stock quote API\" --limit 10","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20842,"output":189,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35015,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772517861872}}
{"type":"message","id":"93f902a8","parentId":"b81a6bbe","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:04:36.854Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_evhl4egmuegu_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Chinese A股 stock quote API\",\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub_io_api.stock.quote\",\n      \"name\": \"Quote\",\n      \"description\": \"Get real-time quote data for US stocks.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Stock symbol\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 3.472,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.hk_connect_stats.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 沪深港通交易统计 (HK Stock Connect Trading Stats)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query Shanghai-Shenzhen-Hong Kong Stock Connect trading statistics from 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database. Covers northbound (沪股通, 深股通) and southbound (港股通沪市, 港股通深市) channels. Returns trading volume, buy/sell amounts, net buy amount, transaction counts, and top-10 active stocks concentration ratios. Supports daily, weekly, monthly, and yearly aggregation. Useful for tracking cross-border capital flows between mainland China and Hong Kong markets.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sdate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Start date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"edate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"End date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"zq\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Aggregation period. Valid values: 'day', 'week', 'month', 'year'. Defaults to 'week'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"lx\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Channel type filter. 'ALL'=all channels, '1'=沪股通, '2'=港股通(沪市), '3'=深股通, '4'=港股通(深市). Defaults to 'ALL'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"bz\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Currency for amounts. Defaults to 'CNY'.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺实时行情 (THS Real-time Quotation)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query real-time quotation data for securities in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, providing real-time market data for financial products including stocks, funds, bonds, and futures, such as real-time prices, trading volumes, price changes, bid/ask quotes, etc. Supports querying various real-time indicators including latest price, price change, trading volume, turnover ratio, market value, and five-level bid/ask quotes.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"indicators\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Indicator list, multiple indicators separated by commas. Options: 'common' (common indicators), 'all' (all indicators), or custom indicator list. Default is 'all'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"codes\": \"300033.SZ,600030.SH\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"fmp.company.quote.get.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"Stock Index Quote\",\n      \"description\": \"Access real-time stock index quotes with the latest price changes, daily highs and lows, volume, and other key metrics for major stock indices around the world.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"The stock symbol of the company (e.g., AAPL for Apple Inc.)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Financial Modeling Prep is a financial data platform that provides real-time and historical stock market data, financial statements, company profiles, and other financial metrics for public companies, private companies, and ETFs.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1404.57,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.036\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financial_modeling_prep.stock.quote.retrieve.v1.822497ca\",\n      \"name\": \"Stock Quote API\",\n      \"description\": \"Access real-time stock quotes with the FMP Stock Quote API. Get up-to-the-minute prices, changes, and volume data for individual stocks. Also access real-time stock index quotes, stay updated with the latest price changes, daily highs and lows, volume, and other key metrics for major stock indices around the world. This API can also be used for commodities, forex, and cryptocurrencies.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Symbol for the asset\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Financial Modeling Prep is a financial data platform that provides real-time and historical stock market data, financial statements, company profiles, and other financial metrics for public companies, private companies, and ETFs.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 994.08,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.113\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financial_modeling_prep.quote_short.retrieve.v1.65790c37\",\n      \"name\": \"Stock Index Short Quote\",\n      \"description\": \"Access concise stock index quotes providing a snapshot of the current price, change, and volume for stock indexes.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Index symbol (e.g., ^GSPC)\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"^GSPC\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Financial Modeling Prep is a financial data platform that provides real-time and historical stock market data, financial statements, company profiles, and other financial metrics for public companies, private companies, and ETFs.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1239.57,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.344\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.company_basics.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 公司基础信息 (Company Basics)\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve the latest (or a specific date) company basics indicators from THS iFinD. Includes company name, industry, comparable/peer companies, concept tags, codes, established date, registration info, main business, and major products.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, comma-separated (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Date, format: 'YYYYMMDD'. Use this field to query historical values. Defaults to latest.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.etf_constituents.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD ETF成分股票列表 (ETF Constituent Stock List)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query the constituent stock list of an ETF from 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database. Returns detailed information about each constituent stock including stock code, name, share quantity, cash substitution flag, subscription/redemption premium ratios and fixed substitution amounts. Useful for analyzing ETF composition and tracking ETF holdings.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"thscode\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"ETF security code, e.g., '510300.SH', '159001.SZ'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Query date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'. Defaults to today.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financial_modeling_prep.aftermarket.quote.retrieve.v1.65b7474a\",\n      \"name\": \"Aftermarket Quote API\",\n      \"description\": \"Access real-time aftermarket quotes for stocks with the FMP Aftermarket Quote API. Track bid and ask prices, volume, and other relevant data outside of regular trading hours.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Stock symbol\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Financial Modeling Prep is a financial data platform that provides real-time and historical stock market data, financial statements, company profiles, and other financial metrics for public companies, private companies, and ETFs.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1355.03,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.001\n      }\n    },\n    {\n     