{"type":"message","id":"fcf4b376","parentId":"93f902a8","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:04:51.629Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The iFinD tool keeps showing up but it has a configuration issue. Let me try to troubleshoot this more directly. The error says \"缺少必需的查询参数: 'codes'\" - which is \"missing required query parameter: codes\" - even though we're passing the codes parameter.\n\nThis is likely a backend issue with how QVeris is forwarding the request to iFinD. Let me try one more thing - maybe the iFinD tool needs the parameters formatted differently, or maybe there's a different version.\n\nActually wait, looking at the search results more carefully, I see there's a tool \"ths_ifind.company_basics.v1\" that also uses `codes` parameter. Let me try that one to see if it works - if it does, then the issue is specifically with the real_time_quotation tool.","thinkingSignature":"47d13ce422d8de1917d51c7184095a71e37b3925e234e7ceda9e589c63552083"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_iwir8vj4t4lj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace && node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs execute ths_ifind.company_basics.v1 --params '{\"codes\":\"002149.SZ\"}'","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":23897,"output":240,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38121,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772517876854}}
