{"type":"message","id":"78682b2b","parentId":"c43a8205","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:05:47.150Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All iFinD tools are having the same issue. The parameters aren't being passed through to the backend. This appears to be a systematic problem with the QVeris iFinD integration.\n\nLet me try one last approach - I'll try to access the stock data through a different mechanism. Maybe I can try the EODHD with different ticker formats or see if there's any other tool that works for Chinese stocks.\n\nActually, I wonder if the EODHD API might work for Chinese stocks using different ticker formats. Let me try.","thinkingSignature":"0e72ff9ccf75996ff1b9a17a93ceb44caf0944a0ad61fe53caed0cba088565cc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j2dqkkwg55dy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace && node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs execute eodhd.live_prices.retrieve.v1.178541d4 --params '{\"ticker\":\"600000.SS\"}'","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":33548,"output":188,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47720,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772517941299}}
