{"type":"message","id":"10706aba","parentId":"1f030928","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:06:06.350Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Same issue with EODHD. This is frustrating - it seems like many of the financial tools in QVeris are having parameter passing issues. Let me try one more thing - Finnhub, which was working well in the search. Let me see if it can give any data.Actually, Finnhub only supports US stocks. Let me try a different search for maybe a different Chinese data provider.\n\nWait - let me think about this differently. Maybe there's something wrong with my parameter passing. Let me try using the exact same format as the example in the tool description.\n\nActually wait - I just realized something. The error says \"缺少必需的路径参数\" (missing required path parameter) vs earlier which said \"缺少必需的查询参数\" (missing required query parameter). These are different types of parameters.\n\nLet me try a totally different approach. Maybe I can try to use another tool that works differently.","thinkingSignature":"5c073502bbafeae4434a9ec8eb29b2a66f5c0472cc65ec03118b667fb1b665d2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tsmc037rujxz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace && node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs search \"real time stock price China Shenzhen Shanghai\" --limit 15","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":33868,"output":249,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48101,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772517948682}}
{"type":"message","id":"58598a70","parentId":"10706aba","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:06:09.415Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_tsmc037rujxz_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"real time stock price China Shenzhen Shanghai\",\n  \"total\": 15,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺实时行情 (THS Real-time Quotation)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query real-time quotation data for securities in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, providing real-time market data for financial products including stocks, funds, bonds, and futures, such as real-time prices, trading volumes, price changes, bid/ask quotes, etc. Supports querying various real-time indicators including latest price, price change, trading volume, turnover ratio, market value, and five-level bid/ask quotes.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"indicators\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Indicator list, multiple indicators separated by commas. Options: 'common' (common indicators), 'all' (all indicators), or custom indicator list. Default is 'all'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"codes\": \"300033.SZ,600030.SH\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.live_prices.retrieve.v1.178541d4\",\n      \"name\": \"Live (Delayed) Stock Prices\",\n      \"description\": \"Retrieve live or delayed stock prices and macroeconomic data.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"ticker\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Ticker symbol with exchange suffix (e.g., AAPL.US).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"s\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Optional filter parameter.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"ticker\": \"AAPL.US\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1248.29,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.938\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.hk_connect_stats.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 沪深港通交易统计 (HK Stock Connect Trading Stats)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query Shanghai-Shenzhen-Hong Kong Stock Connect trading statistics from 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database. Covers northbound (沪股通, 深股通) and southbound (港股通沪市, 港股通深市) channels. Returns trading volume, buy/sell amounts, net buy amount, transaction counts, and top-10 active stocks concentration ratios. Supports daily, weekly, monthly, and yearly aggregation. Useful for tracking cross-border capital flows between mainland China and Hong Kong markets.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sdate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Start date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"edate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"End date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"zq\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Aggregation period. Valid values: 'day', 'week', 'month', 'year'. Defaults to 'week'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"lx\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Channel type filter. 'ALL'=all channels, '1'=沪股通, '2'=港股通(沪市), '3'=深股通, '4'=港股通(深市). Defaults to 'ALL'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"bz\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Currency for amounts. Defaults to 'CNY'.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"eodhd.real_time.retrieve.v1.3b8a5cf8\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Real-Time (Delayed) Stock Prices\",\n      \"description\": \"Fetch real-time price data for a specified cryptocurrency pair.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Stock ticker symbol with exchange suffix (e.g., AAPL.US)\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"fmt\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Response format\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"json\",\n            \"csv\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"EUR.FOREX\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1154.75,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.867\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financial_modeling_prep.stock.quote.retrieve.v1.822497ca\",\n      \"name\": \"Stock Quote API\",\n      \"description\": \"Access real-time stock quotes with the FMP Stock Quote API. Get up-to-the-minute prices, changes, and volume data for individual stocks. Also access real-time stock index quotes, stay updated with the latest price changes, daily highs and lows, volume, and other key metrics for major stock indices around the world. This API can also be used for commodities, forex, and cryptocurrencies.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Symbol for the asset\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Financial Modeling Prep is a financial data platform that provides real-time and historical stock market data, financial statements, company profiles, and other financial metrics for public companies, private companies, and ETFs.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 994.08,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.113\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financial_modeling_prep.quote_short.retrieve.v1.65790c37\",\n      \"name\": \"Stock Index Short Quote\",\n      \"description\": \"Access concise stock index quotes providing a snapshot of the current price, change, and volume for stock indexes.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Index symbol (e.g., ^GSPC)\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"^GSPC\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Financial Modeling Prep is a financial data platform that provides real-time and historical stock market data, financial statements, company profiles, and other financial metrics for public companies, private companies, and ETFs.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1239.57,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.344\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"financial_modeling_prep.quote_short.retrieve.v1.729a84c2\",\n      \"name\": \"Stock Index Short Quote\",\n      \"description\": \"Get quick snapshots of real-time stock quotes with the FMP Stock Quote Short API. Access key stock data like current price, volume, and price changes for instant market insights.; Access concise stock index quotes with the Stock Index Short Quote API. This API provides a snapshot of the current price, change, and volume for stock indexes, making it ideal for users who need a quick overview of market movements. Also used for commodities, forex, cryptocurrencies.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Symbol for the asset\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"^GSPC\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Financial Modeling Prep is a financial data platform that provides real-time and historical stock market data, financial statements, company profiles, and other financial metrics for public companies, private companies, and ETFs.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1197.39,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.202\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub_io_api.stock.quote\",\n      \"name\": \"Quote\",\n      \"description\": \"Get real-time quote data for US stocks.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Stock symbol\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 3.472,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"fmp.company.quote.get.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"Stock Index Quote\",\n      \"description\": \"Access real-time stock index quotes with the latest price changes, daily highs and lows, volume, and other key metrics for major stock indices around the world.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"The stock symbol of the company (e.g., AAPL for Apple Inc.)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Financial Modeling Prep is a financial data platform that provides real-time and historical stock market data, financial statements, company profiles, and other financial metrics for public companies, private companies, and ETFs.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1404.57,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.036\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.quotation.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 同花顺行情 (历史+实时) (THS Quotation)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query historical and real-time quotation data for securities in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, supporting price, trading volume, turnover ratio, and other indicators for various financial products including stocks, funds, bonds, and futures.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"codes\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"indicators\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Indicator list, comma-separated. Options: 'common' (common indicators), 'all' (all indicators), or custom list. Default is 'all'. Applies to both history and real-time calls.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"startdate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Start date, formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"enddate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"End date, formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"interval\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Time period: 'D' (daily), 'W' (weekly), 'M' (monthly), 'Q' (quarterly), 'S' (semi-annual), 'Y' (yearly), default 'D'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"cps\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Adjustment method: '1' (no adjustment), '2' (forward), '3' (backward), '6' (forward cash dividend), '7' (backward cash dividend), default '1'\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"fill\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Non-trading day handling: 'Previous' (use previous data), 'Blank' (empty), default 'Previous'\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.stock.marketstatus.retrieve.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"Market Status\",\n      \"description\": \"Get current market status for global exchanges (whether exchanges are open or close).\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"exchange\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Exchange code.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"exchange\": \"US\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 3.168,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.stock.marketstatus.execute.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"Market Status\",\n      \"description\": \"Get current market status for global exchanges (whether exchanges are open or close).\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"exchange\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n    