{"type":"message","id":"cee0139c","parentId":"8546643a","timestamp":"2026-03-03T06:07:49.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Same issue. This confirms that QVeris has a systemic problem with its tool execution - the parameters are not being forwarded correctly. This appears to be a backend issue with the QVeris API itself.Given that:\n1. Browser is forbidden\n2. QVeris is required\n3. The iFinD (同花顺) tool that should provide Chinese stock data has a configuration error\n4. All other financial tools also have the same parameter passing issue\n\nI need to inform the user about this situation. Unfortunately, I cannot retrieve the stock prices through QVeris at this moment due to what appears to be a backend service issue.","thinkingSignature":"c8912ed8f7343785abc63381f7b4a7a5a67db901b862acb227a983dba9ae32dc"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，无法获取持仓实时股价。\n\n**问题原因：** QVeris 的同花顺 (iFinD) 实时行情接口出现配置错误，所有金融工具都存在参数无法正确传递的技术问题。已尝试：\n- iFinD 实时行情 `ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1`\n- iFinD 历史+实时行情 `ths_ifind.quotation.v1`  \n- EODHD、Finnhub、Yahoo Finance 等其他金融数据工具\n\n全部返回 `configuration_error: 缺少必需的查询参数: 'codes'`\n\n这是 QVeris 服务端问题，需要联系 QVeris 支持排查后端集成。建议暂时通过同花顺官方 APP/网站查看以上三只股票的实时行情：\n- **002149.SZ** 西部材料\n- **601899.SH** 鑫科材料  \n- **601975.SH** 招商公路"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":42076,"output":316,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56376,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772518055361}}
